name: A Day In The Life Of A Stapler
description: An unflinching, uncompromising account of the beginnings of sexual awakenings within the mind of a household object which we too rarely sexualise. A journey through the conflicts and chaos in the lives of every sentient being, focussed through the naive, trusting personality of an unsuspecting young stapler on the cusp of adulthood. WARNING: contains adult themes and erotic imagery.
